{"word":"ἐλπίς","slug":"ἐλπίς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐλπίς, ίδος, ἡ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ s.\">s.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ prec.\">prec.</a>]<b><p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>1.</pp></b> ‘a state of looking forward to <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> that is desirable’, <b>hope, expectation <a href='B:510 2:26'>Ac 2:26</a>; <a href='B:510 16:19'>16:19</a>; <a href='B:520 4:18'>Ro 4:18</a>; <a href='B:520 8:20'>8:20</a>; <a href='B:530 9:10'>1 Cor 9:10</a>; <a href='B:540 1:7'>2 Cor 1:7</a>.</b> With special <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ ref.\">ref.</a> to hope of believers <b><a href='B:510 26:6'>Ac 26:6</a>; <a href='B:520 5:4'>Ro 5:4f</a>; <a href='B:530 13:13'>1 Cor 13:13</a>; <a href='B:580 1:23'>Col 1:23</a>; <a href='B:650 3:6'>Hb 3:6</a>; <a href='B:670 1:3'>1 Pt 1:3</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>2.</pp></b> ‘basis of firm expectation’, <b>hope <a href='B:580 1:27'>Col 1:27</a>; <a href='B:590 2:19'>1 Th 2:19</a>; <a href='B:610 1:1'>1 Ti 1:1</a>.<p class=\"pp1\"/>—<pp>3.</pp></b> ‘<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ someth.\">someth.</a> hoped for’, <b>hope <a href='B:520 8:24'>Ro 8:24</a>; <a href='B:650 6:18'>Hb 6:18</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐλπίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:Ἐλύμας\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}